VERSION 1
WHEN CURRENT_FILE_MATCHES /\bAsyncStorage\.(?:setItem|multiSet)\s*\(/i
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:AsyncStorage\.(?:setItem|multiSet).*(?:password|token|secret|key|auth|credential)
OBSERVE PROJECT_HAS_GLOB **/package.json AS package_manifests
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects AsyncStorage use for sensitive values such as tokens or credentials.
TRACE Mobile RDL pilot evaluated sensitive AsyncStorage usage while allowing the project package manifest to provide extra context.
